tourBios.otherCarHigh: Four-year letterman at Lafayette College was co-captain of the golf team as a senior. First-team All-Patriot League as a sophomore and second-team selection in both junior and seniors seasons. Team captured Patriot League championship in 2010.
tourBios.personal: Involved with Amanda McPherson Foundation...Favorite vacation spot is Hawaii...Favorite athletes are Kobe Bryant and Tiger Woods, while favorite teams are the Los Angeles Lakers and San Diego Chargers...All-conference basketball player in high school.

dyn.dynResults: His best finish on the PGA TOUR Canada was T32nd in 2014 at the ATB Financial Classic.
dyn.dynStats: He ranks 58th in Par 3 Birdie or Better Leaders on the PGA TOUR Canada.
